snippet.title: Kabhi Main Kabhi Tum Episode 32 | Fahad Mustafa | Hania Aamir | 28 Oct 2024  (Eng Sub) | ARY Digital
snippet.description:
Watch all the episode of Kabhi Main Kabhi Tum here: https://bit.ly/3zNNsGu

Kabhi Main Kabhi Tum | Episode 32 | Digitally Presented by Master Paints , foodpanda , Sunsilk & Skin White | Fahad Mustafa | Hania Aamir | 28 October 2024 | ARY Digital Drama 

The drama revolves around the concept of ‘Opposites Attract’ where Hania aka Sharjeena will portray the role of a bibliophile, topper and a sorted girl with a practical approach while Fahad’s character is a little laid-back.

Writer: Farhat Ishtiaq
Directed by: Badar Mehmood
 
Cast:
Fahad Mustafa as Mustafa
Hania Aamir as Sharjeena
Emmad Irfani as Adeel
Javed Sheikh as Iftekhar 
Bushra Ansari as Shagufta
Maya Khan as Sidra
Naeema Butt as Rubab
Tauseeq Haider,
Yousuf Bashir Qureshi.

Hey Guys, 
Welcome to my YouTube Channel,
I'm Jonathan Amaral, you might know me as Jonathan Gaming.
I started my professional Esports Career competing in Pubg Mobile Championships (Now BGMI),
Since the start of my career, I have been consistent with my gameplay and always been working hard to achieve my goals via winning Domestic/Global Championships. 
"The only player you should try to be better than is the player you were yesterday."
I Stream BGMI regularly, I also enjoy playing Valorant and other fun games once in a while!
I upload videos regarding Tutorials for BGMI, Funny Highlights, Intense Fights, Crate Openings, Vlogs, etc.

snippet.title: MIXTURE Snack | DIWALI Special Traditional Mixture Recipe Cooking In Village | South Indian Snacks
snippet.description:
Mixture Recipe is a popular snack recipe in South India, especially in Tamil Nadu, Kerala and Karnataka. Today, we are cooking this recipe as a Diwali Special. The specialty of this snack is its mixed taste. 

To enhance the flavor of this mixture, we use Boondi, Fried Nuts, Fried Spices, and other healthy ingredients, along with Omappodi.

The taste is memorable!

Jaan Nisar 2nd Last Episode 64 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 25th October 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

snippet.title: Ek Diwali Aisi Bhi | Biggest Crossover of Take A Break
snippet.description:
Ever wondered how those Diwali sketches come to life? In our latest comedy video, "Ek Diwali Aisi Bhi," we take you behind the scenes for a hilarious peek into our writers' room as they brainstorm ideas for a Diwali sketch! 🎆🤣
Join our team of writers as they toss around the most outlandish, over-the-top, and downright ridiculous ideas for the ultimate Diwali-themed video. From traditional family gatherings gone hilariously wrong to bizarre plot twists involving our IP's, each suggestion brings its own flavor of chaos and comedy.

#kaamwalibai #takeabreak #shortsbreak

Producer - Pratik Thakur

snippet.title: Thozha - Back to Back comedy scene 2 | Karthi | Nagarjuna | Vivek | Tammanah | Adithya TV
snippet.description:
The story revolves around Vikramadhitya (Nagarjuna) a quadriplegic billionaire, and Seenu, (Karthi) his ex-convict caretaker. Circumstances in their life teach them the value of relationships over money. 

Thozha is a 2016 movie . It was released in both Telugu and Tamil languages. Its name in Telugu is Oppri . The film is a remake of the French film The Intouchables . The film stars Karthik Sivakumar , Nagarsuna , Tamannaah , Prakasu Rasu , Vivek , Anushka , Seyashuda , Sireyya . The film is directed by Vamsi Baidipalli and produced by Prasad V Potluri.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Minku hai bahut bada khiladi (played by Amit Bhadana) jo ek sath 3-3 girlfriends ko ghuma raha hai aur unke gifts aur paise kha raha hai. Lekin ek din Minku ki life mein aa jata hai bhuchal jab ek girlfriend uske samne rakh deti hai ek demand. Ye sabhi ladkiyan rehti hai ek hi Girls Hostel mein. Kaise bachayega Minku apni jaan? snippet.title: 1 ലക്ഷം മുടക്കി മൈക്കിൾ ഒരു കാർ
snippet.description:
***Connect With Us**

Facebook Page: https://www.facebook.com/ebulljet
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/e_bull_jet
Twitter: https://twitter.com/EBINVAR11589819
TikTok:  https://www.tiktok.com/@ebulljet

CONTACT US: 
Whatsapp no: https://wa.me/919496502055

***About Our Channel***

Van life is very common in western countries. So in this channel at E Bull Jet, we are featuring van life in India. This channel will showcase the real-life in India and nearby countries.

We are Abin and Libin, siblings belonging to Irutty, a locality in Kannur District of Kerala, India. We aim to explore India and nearby countries in a van that's converted into a home. In this journey, we will sleep, cook, and travel in our van and will ex cover places at minimal expenses.  

We would like to bring our Van life though this channel - E BULL JET

പാശ്ചാത്യ രാജ്യങ്ങളിൽ ഉള്ള പോലെ നമ്മുടെ രാജ്യത്തും ഒരു വാൻ ലൈഫ് നടത്തുകയും അതിന്റെ മാസ്മരിക കാഴ്ചകൾ പ്രിയപെട്ടവരിലേക്ക് എത്തിക്കുകയും ആണ് 'ഈ ബുൾ ജെറ്റ്' എന്ന ഈ കൊച്ചു ചാനൽ കൊണ്ട് ഞങ്ങൾ ഉദ്ദേശിക്കുന്നത്.

കണ്ണൂർ ജില്ലയിലെ ഇരുട്ടി എന്ന പ്രദേശത്തു ജീവിക്കുന്ന സഹോദരങ്ങളാണ് ഞങ്ങൾ, പേര് എബിൻ, ലിബിൻ. നമ്മുടെ രാജ്യവും, അയാൾ രാജ്യങ്ങളും കുറഞ്ഞ ചിലവിൽ കാണുക എന്നതാണ് ലക്ഷ്യം. അതിനായി ഒരു മിനി വാൻ ഞങ്ങൾ വീടാക്കി മാറ്റി അതിൽ യാത്ര ചെയുന്നു, വഴിയിൽ പാചകം ചെയ്തു കുറഞ്ഞു ചിലവിൽ ലോകം കാണുക എന്നതാണ് ലക്ഷ്യം. 

ഞങ്ങൾ കാണുന്നതും കേള്കുന്നതുമായ കാര്യങ്ങൾ ഈ ചാനലിൽ കൂടെ പങ്കുവെക്കുക എന്നതാണ് ലക്ഷ്യം.

PLEASE SUBSCRIBE TO THIS CHANNEL AND ENABLE NOTIFICATIONS: 
"Van Life Is our Passion"
"Your dream our world
This is our vision and mission - E BULL JET

Dream with Us. Thank You. :)

snippet.title: Dr. Hathi की हँसी पर Jetha का Reaction | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Old Gems
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

In this episode, Taarak comes up with an idea to ask Dr. Hathi and his family to leave Gokuldham Society. Everyone is puzzled by Dr. Hathi's constant laughter. It’s revealed at the end that the ladoos he ate in the morning were made with bhang, causing the laughter! Meanwhile, Mehta has a conversation with Anjali about being patriotic. What will happen next? Watch to find out.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 305
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #jethatheroastking #tmkocmemes #tmkocold #taarakmehta #jethalalcomedy #dayaben #bhide #popatlal #babitaji #comedyshow #comedyvideo #comedymemes 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Taarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the episodes of 'Old Gems' : 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTNuXI_HVBQHzw7Odv4Fj0A

Dr. Hathi की हंसी पर Jetha का Reaction? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Old Gems

Trivikram Srinivas Speech @ Lucky Baskhar Pre-Release Event | Dulquer Salmaan, Meenakshi, Venky Atluri | GV Prakash Kumar | Naga Vamsi 

An absolute stunner and a diligent performer, Rowdy #VijayDeverakonda and our Darling Director #Trivikram garu will be gracing the Pre-release event of #LuckyBaskhar 🤩❤️‍🔥

#LuckyBaskhar is our upcoming film Starring Dulquer Salmaan, Meenakshi Chaudhary in Lead Roles. Written & Directed by Venky Atluri. Music by GV Prakash Kumar. Cinematography by Nimish Ravi. Editing by Navin Nooli. Produced by Naga Vamsi S & Sai Soujanya Under Sithara Entertainments & Fortune Four Cinemas. Presented by Srikara Studios. Releasing this October 31st in Telugu, Malayalam, Hindi, Tamil & Kannada Languages.

Cast & Crew Details:

Movie: Lucky Baskhar 
Stars: Dulquer Salmaan, Meenakshi Chaudhary

snippet.title: No Filter: Nia Sharma
snippet.description:
Hello Ji, Namaste Dooston Bharti TV Podcast Mein Aapka Fir Se Swagat Hai!

इस Episode में हम Nia Sharma के Diverse Life को Explore करते हैं, जिसमें उनकी Journey Daily Soaps से लेकर एक Fashion Icon तक का सफर शामिल है। Nia अपने Acting Career की शुरुआत, Evolving TV industry के बारे में अपने Views, और Fashion पर अपने Thoughts को Candid तरीके से Share करेंगी। वह अपने दो सबसे अच्छे Friends के साथ अपने Equation के बारे में भी बात करेंगी, जिन्हें वह प्यार से "Kids" कहती हैं। Marriage, Laughter Shows, और Sudesh Lehri के साथ काम करने के अपने Experience को भी Express करेंगी। हम उनकी Confidence, Male Attention को कैसे Handle करती हैं, और Brands के साथ उनके Negotiation के Experience पर भी चर्चा करेंगे। Nia अपने भाई, Vinay Sharma के साथ अपने Relation के बारे में भी बात करेंगी, और किस तरह के Projects पर वह आगे काम करना चाहती हैं इस पर भी चर्चा होगी। Nia यह भी बताएंगी कि क्या उन्हें Cooking आती है, और YouTube और 'Laughter Chef' Show पर अपनी राय भी देंगी। अंत में, हम उनके Anchoring और Hosting को लेकर उनके Perspective को भी Explore करेंगे!

Yeh Episode Nia Sharma Ke Life Aur Personality Ki Ek Khubsurat Jhalak Hai, Dekhte Rahiye Bharti TV!

#niasharma #bhartisingh #harshlimbachiya  #lolpodcast #podcast

snippet.title: Purvi को ढूंढने में Abhijeet-Daya ने लगाया पूरा दम | CID | सी.आई.डी. | Latest Episode | 26 Oct 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

The inhabitants of a society call CID to complain about one of their inhabitants named Vikram who has a gun with him. CID goes into interrogating and in a fight between Daya and Vikram, Vikram gets shot. Upon further investigation in his flat, CID finds photographs of victims who have been tied up. What does Vikram do? Watch this episode to find out.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 840
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2024 #LatestTV #LatestFromTV #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #latestcid #cid #cidlatestepisode#cidnewepisode #hinditvserial #latestepisode #newepisode #tvserial #hindiserial #hindishow #tvshow #livcrime #dayaaurabhijeetkidosti

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Daya Aur Abhijeet Ki Dosti' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIVH-HhI_BSk3AH2q5PUHy_R

Lyrics-
Labhde firde maame tere pakke tikaane ve,
Laggu 26 ja 307 eh rabb hi jane ve,
Ho leke jamanat hafte vich aau bahar rakane ni,
Ho uthde behnde leader’an naal mere yaar rakane ni,
Ve laa laa naake sane gaddi tainu chakkan nu firde,
Ho darr na jattiye sade layi koi vadda masla nahi,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Jadd vi turde kafla naal tu leke turde ve,
Sheh ki jatt pendi na dasan di kade lod billo,
Dil dul ta ve lagda tera tutt da hona ni,
Kade kade vajjdiye pinde nu bas tod billo,
Taur Tappe to bina hor das ki ki kadh da o,
Kade kadai kande kade kadai tasla’an ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Darda vakil ve aulakha tera case koi fadd da nahi,
Saddi aakh kadhdiye kalli jane kaam koi khad da nahi,
Oh jadd tak ghar ni mud da ve dil jeha dar da rehnda ae,
Tere te hi marda aaukha saukha marda nahi,
Triple 0 1 LC vich kon ya hunda ve,
Jay virk jahe pakke yaar te nale pakkiya rafla ni,
Ve Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Tainu firde chakkan nu pale par tu thalle ni lagda,
Tahi ta tere aale jatt de utte lagde ni,
Ve dino dini tera tam jham jeha vadh da janda ae,
Mehar babe di sir te balliye tahio dabde nahi,
Vairi sadde ne naale tere te aakh ji rakde ne,
Hundiya ni tavi karde ne tere jatt diya nakla ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni…
